<p><strong>Understanding <em>our Ego barrier:</em></strong></p>

<p>Remember that feeling we talked about in the beginning? That moment when you felt as if your personal capabilities, <em>your</em> <em>value</em> as a contributing member of the group felt threatened. That is your ego barrier. Before we go on and blame ourselves for behaving as such we first need to understand that this is already programmed in our genes and the only way through is around.</p>

