<p><strong>Why should I care about the Ego barrier?</strong></p>

<p>While it would be excellent to keep the irrational monkey at home and just carry with us the executive, we cannot cage the monkey and they both form part of our decision-making processes. They constantly argue against each other and strive to battle for our attention.</p>

